divs: Sighting DetailsTHIS PICS WHERE TAKEN FROM MY CELL PHONE ON A BASICALLY CLOUDLESS DAY IN CHANDLER, I WAS DRIVING BACK TO MY OLD HOUSE WHEN NOTICED ABOVE SOME OF THE HOUSES, A PARTICULAR AND PERFECT CLOUD IN A CIRCLE SHAPE.I GOT OF MY CAR AND TOOK A QUICK PICTURE, UNFORTUNATELY MY CELLPHONE BATTERY WAS DYING AND COULDN'T TAKE MORE.i DECIDED TO DRIVE CLOSER TO THE CLOUD AND THEN I WAS ABLE TO SEE A DARKER SHAPE WITHIN THE CLOUD AND ALSO NOTICED ANOTHER ONE TO THE WEST OF THE FIRST ONE.LATER THAT NIGHT I DOWNLOADED THE PICTURE ON MY LAPTOP AND WAS ABLE TO ZOOM IT AND I DO FEEL I CAUGHT SOMETHING THAT I CAN'T EXPLAIN.THE CLOUD ONLY LASTED APROX LIKE 8 TO 10 MIN AND THEN IT WAS GONE.LOOKING AT THE PICTURES WITH THE ZOOM I NOTICED THAT EACH OBJECT HAS R ABOVE THEM OR DIAGONALLY LIKE 200 OR 300 FEET ABOVE THEM TO THE WEST A BLACK SPHERE. PLEASE LET ME KNOW IF THIS IS WHAT I THINK IT IS OR JUST AN EFFECT FROM THE SUN???? MY SON AND I WILL REALLY APPRECIATE YOUR RESPONSE. THANK YOU!!
Summary: DRIVING BACK HOME ON A CLEAR DAY AND NOTICED CICLED CLOUD FORMATION
